## Installation

```bash
# 1. Clone
git clone https://github.com/Bhanks434/bhanks-base-project
cd bhanks-base-project

# 2. Install dependencies
npm install

# 3. Set up environment
cp .env.example .env
# Edit .env with your API keys

# 4. Run locally
npm run dev
```

## Smart contract development

```bash
# Compile contracts
npx hardhat compile

# Run tests
npx hardhat test

# Deploy to Base Sepolia
npx hardhat run scripts/deployToken.js --network baseSepolia
```